      "originalText": "CC: 👍 Agreed — one convention, document it, follow it.\n   That's the doc-surface principle on this canvas:\n   ONE diagram/ schema per level, no per-author variants.\n   This file proves the loop works.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
